  "title": "Crafting Recipes For Create",
  "description": "This Mod Allows You To Craft Chipped Block With The Create Mod",
  "body": "<h1>🛠️ Craft Chipped Blocks Using the Power of Create!</h1>\n<p>Want to spice up your builds with <strong>Chipped</strong> blocks, but love using <strong>Create</strong> for all your crafting automation? This mod brings the best of both worlds!<br><strong>Now you can craft Chipped blocks using the machinery and mechanics from the Create mod.</strong> It's time to automate your aesthetic!</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>🔧 Requirements</h2>\n<p>To use this mod, you'll need both the <strong>Create</strong> and <strong>Chipped</strong> mods installed. Choose your version below:</p>\n<h3><img src=\"https://files.minecraftforge.net/static/images/favicon-32x32.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\">&nbsp; Create + Forge (1.20.1 and 1.19.2)</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/create\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/create_vector.svg\" alt=\"Create\"></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/chipped/files/all?page=1&amp;pageSize=20&amp;gameVersionTypeId=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BrayDog2010/devins-badges/ab6c523498e18dcf2d63411e7522aa3a27d0a84c/assets/cozy/requires/chipped_forge_vector.svg\" alt=\"Chipped Forge\"></a></p>\n<h3><img src=\"https://fabricmc.net/assets/favicon.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\">&nbsp; Create + Fabric (1.20.1 and 1.19.2)</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/create-fabric\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/create-fabric_vector.svg\" alt=\"Create Fabric\"></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/chipped/files/all?page=1&amp;pageSize=20&amp;gameVersionTypeId=4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BrayDog2010/devins-badges/ab6c523498e18dcf2d63411e7522aa3a27d0a84c/assets/cozy/requires/chipped_fabric_vector.svg\" alt=\"Chipped Fabric\"></a></p>\n<h3><img src=\"https://neoforged.net/img/authors/neoforged.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\">&nbsp; Create + NeoForge (1.21.1 and 1.20.1) Still need Chipped But Don't Have Icon</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/create\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/create_vector.svg\" alt=\"Create NeoForge\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>📦 Other Palces To Download</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/crafting-recipes-for-create\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3.2.0/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\" alt=\"Curseforge\" height=\"56\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>📦 Source And Issues</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/BrayDog2010/Crafting-Recipes-For-Create\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3.2.0/assets/cozy/available/github_vector.svg\" alt=\"Github\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>✨ Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Seamlessly integrates Chipped blocks into the Create mod's crafting systems</li>\n<li>Compatible with both Forge, Fabric, and NeoForge loaders</li>\n<li>Supports Minecraft versions <strong>1.20.1</strong>, <strong>1.19.2, and 1.21.1 (NeoForge Only)</strong></li>\n<li>Great for builders and automation enthusiasts alike</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>💬 \"Why make blocks manually when you can engineer them into existence?\"</p>",
